{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "1d8a15dc-d6bb-47ab-a779-83a3e930f8ee",
    "name": "Hermes Agent API Server",
    "description": "来源: gateway/platforms/api_server.py。\n\n本 Collection 覆盖该文件对外暴露的全部 HTTP API，并在请求描述中包含入参/出参说明。\n\n认证:\n- 受保护接口需携带 `Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}`\n- 当服务端未配置 API key 时，认证可被跳过（仅建议本地环境）\n\nSSE 重点:\n- `POST /v1/chat/completions` 当 `stream=true` 时返回 SSE\n- `POST /v1/responses` 当 `stream=true` 时返回 SSE\n- `GET /v1/runs/{run_id}/events` 固定返回 SSE\n\n建议先设置变量 `baseUrl` 与 `apiKey` 再执行。",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://127.0.0.1:8642"
    },
    {
      "key": "apiKey",
      "value": "replace-with-api-server-key"
    },
    {
      "key": "responseId",
      "value": "resp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx"
    },
    {
      "key": "runId",
      "value": "run_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx"
    },
    {
      "key": "jobId",
      "value": "0123456789ab"
    },
    {
      "key": "sessionId",
      "value": "demo-session-id"
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": "10001"
    }
  ],
