            "description": "用途: 按会话 ID 查询问答轮次列表（按 turn_no 升序，第 1 轮在上）。\n\n入参:\n- Path: session_id — 支持以下任一形式:\n  - 数据库自增 id (如 1)\n  - session_uid\n  - hermes_session_id (X-Hermes-Session-Id)\n\n出参(200):\n- object: \"list\"\n- session: object (会话元数据)\n- total: number\n- turns: array (按 turn_no ASC)\n  - turn_no, question_text, answer_text\n  - status: answered|timeout|error|interrupted\n  - error_message, created_at\n\n出参(404): 会话不存在\n出参(503): MySQL 未启用或不可用"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": "{\n  \"object\": \"list\",\n  \"session\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"session_uid\": \"a1b2c3d4e5f6...\",\n    \"hermes_session_id\": \"sess_abc123\",\n    \"user_id\": \"10001\",\n    \"channel\": \"api_server\"\n  },\n  \"total\": 2,\n  \"turns\": [\n    {\n      \"turn_no\": 1,\n      \"question_text\": \"你好\",\n      \"answer_text\": \"你好，我是 Hermes\",\n      \"status\": \"answered\",\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-05-17T10:00:01\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"turn_no\": 2,\n      \"question_text\": \"第二条问题\",\n      \"answer_text\": \"第二条回答\",\n      \"status\": \"answered\",\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-05-17T10:05:01\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
